          "code": "SawOsc a => Gain mix => dac;\nSawOsc b => mix;\nwhile (true) { hostFreq * 1.25 => a.freq; hostFreq * 1.253 => b.freq; 0.14 * hostGain * hostStateGain * hostTrackGain => mix.gain; 1::sample => now; }",
