          "code": "giSine ftgen 1, 0, 4096, 10, 1\ninstr 1\n kfreq chnget \"hostFreq\"\n kgain chnget \"hostGain\"\n a1 oscili kgain * 0.22, kfreq * 8, giSine\n outs a1, a1\nendin",
